Me solte, menino!

282
00:13:17,083 --> 00:13:18,167
Saia!

283
00:13:21,959 --> 00:13:22,959
Olhem!

284
00:13:23,083 --> 00:13:25,083
Vai explodir!
Temos que sair daqui!

285
00:13:28,042 --> 00:13:29,250
O meu pé ficou preso.

286
00:13:29,417 --> 00:13:32,292
